Dialogue: 1,0:01:43.74,0:01:47.83,OP2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\bord0\blur0.6\4a&HFF&\c&H30D1EE&}И {\c&HFFFFFF&}в {\c&H30D1EE&}битве {\c&HFFFFFF&}за {\c&H30D1EE&}свободу {\c&HFFFFFF&}ты {\c&H30D1EE&}сердце {\c&HFFFFFF&}храни
